{"tid":497522,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"殘障支那機OnePlus 5 及 5T 睇唔到高清串流","createTime":"2017-12-13T00:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T05:51:54.000Z","uid":55951,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4a1eff4d9d06d093a3a0b416b48767837ae695","tid":497522,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"OnePlus 新機 OnePlus 5 以及 OnePlus 5T 睇落幾正，係人都知，但係佢有個缺陷，大家第一下可能會聯想到無限 Reboot，又或者電池有問題？咁你就估錯了，事關今次呢個缺陷，令到用家唔能夠使用 Apps 睇高清串流影片。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日，有邊個唔會用手機上 YouTube、Netflix，又或者用 Google Play Movie 買片睇，但係有 OnePlus 討論區成員發現：OnePlus 5 以及 OnePlus 5T 均未能於使用熱門串流影片 Apps 播放高清影片，原因是手機並未得到 Widevine 的一級認證。無呢個認證，就唔能夠於裝置上透過呢類影片 Apps 播放高清影片。OnePlus 方面就回應指，佢地會於未來透過手機更新為手機加入 Widevine 的一級認證，以便用家收看高清串流影片，但未有提及具體時間。仲未買機的話，可能要三思，又或者等多一等喇。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=16122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fnews2.php%3Fid%3D16122&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=478c6810\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=16122</a><br />\n<br />\n垃圾奧普oneplus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb1e5b71e174c012f0c15e28db39fe1ef66ef48","tid":497522,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"oneplus always settle"},{"pid":"cd0d97028c0746c966ae7f91bd98e07406082908","tid":497522,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"但係啲外國youtuber 唔係吹到好撚靚呀,<br />\n好撚快呀, 好撚順呀之類?<br />\n點知係個5&quot; MOON 入面分唔到720P 同1080P?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05b8d3ed6f8d1f564f0a0999c43b431400f7187","tid":497522,"uid":55951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20