e":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"點解我睇到1080p嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2446599025981d04c52c3a85167ca48ef290bb6a","tid":497522,"uid":23677,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>nokia都冇喎 點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主 : 臭蟲論收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n咁請問同oppoplus無有咩關係？</blockquote><br />\n咁請問nokia係咪殘障?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試完無hd未係殘障囉<br />\n有嘅話點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有既咪唔係殘障手機囉 咁你想點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/205347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F205347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e31af9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/205356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F205356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a9afb41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n算唔算有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;It's come to my attention (as my 5T is being shipped) that the 5T, as well as other OnePlus devices, do not have the Widevine L1 Certification required to be able to watch HD content from DRM protected services such as Netflix, Amazon Prime, and Google Play Movies (<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube is not affected</strong></span>).<br />\n<br />\nI would like to know why a $500 phone is not capable of fully utilizing these very popular services and if there are any plans to rectify this clearly ridiculous issue. I am massively surprised this has not been brought up in reviews/not had a bigger fuss made about as this is completely unacceptable for a brand that is now well established!&quot;-whatthefunk, OnePlus forum<br />\n<br />\n睇少d 垃圾中文媒體網啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317f0e8b0ede4e3e6826094f7ffd1d5816e02bea","tid":497522,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n樓主 : 臭蟲論收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n咁請問同oppoplus無有咩關係？</blockquote><br />\n咁請問nokia係咪殘障?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試完無hd未係殘障囉<br />\n有嘅話點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有既咪唔係殘障手機囉 咁你想點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/205347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F205347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e31af9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/205356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F205356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a9afb41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n算唔算有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;It's come to my attention (as my 5T is being shipped) that the 5T, as well as other OnePlus devices, do not have the Widevine L1 Certification required to be able to watch HD content from DRM protected services such as Netflix, Amazon Prime, and Google Play Movies (<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube is not affected</strong></span>).<br />\n<br />\nI would like to know why a $500 phone is not capable of fully utilizing these very popular services and if there are any plans to rectify this clearly ridiculous issue. I am massively surprised this has not been brought up in reviews/not had a bigger fuss made about as this is completely unacceptable for a brand that is now well established!&quot;-whatthefunk, OnePlus forum<br />\n<br />\n睇少d 垃圾中文媒體網啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我下面個係Netflix喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75959bdc87f888408f424d34c1ad8c99b21e724","tid":497522,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"支那仔成日想轉移視線去其他機度<br />\n究竟悶唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c66b388698e9144c5bd45a0ee59659977f0ad0","tid":497522,"uid":123927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f75959bdc87f888408f424d34c1ad8c99b21e724","tid":497522,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"支那仔成日想轉移視線去其他機度<br />\n究竟悶唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"oh"},{"pid":"bc62dad35476b1b4c5bf7801c8d0a1ed933598d1","tid":497522,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}